flowchart LR
  A[Author schema v2<br/>in producer repo] --> B[Local diff vs<br/>registered v1]
  B --> C{Compatibility<br/>check}
  C -- BACKWARD<br/>fails --> X[Block CI<br/>fix or version bump]
  C -- BACKWARD<br/>passes --> D[Register v2<br/>at schema registry]
  D --> E1[Roll out new consumers<br/>that understand v1 and v2]
  E1 --> E2[Roll out producers<br/>emitting v2]
  E2 --> F[Drain remaining v1<br/>events from topic]
  F --> G{Breaking change<br/>required?}
  G -- no --> H[Optional cleanup:<br/>retire upcaster in consumer]
  G -- yes --> I[Publish new event type<br/>OrderPlacedV2]
  I --> J[Run V1 and V2<br/>in parallel for window]
  J --> K[Switch consumers<br/>to V2; retire V1]
